### Create study plan
POST http://localhost:8081/api/study/plans
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "subject": "数据结构",
  "examDate": "2026-06-20",
  "currentLevel": "链表和二叉树比较薄弱",
  "dailyMinutes": 90,
  "targetScore": 85
}

### List study plans
GET http://localhost:8081/api/study/plans

### Get study plan detail
# Replace {planId} with the planId returned by create/list API.
GET http://localhost:8081/api/study/plans/{planId}

### Submit study feedback
# Replace {planId} and taskId with real values returned by the detail API.
POST http://localhost:8081/api/study/plans/{planId}/feedback
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "taskId": 1,
  "completed": false,
  "difficulty": "HARD",
  "problem": "二叉树递归遍历不熟"
}

### Adjust study plan
# Replace {planId} with the real planId.
POST http://localhost:8081/api/study/plans/{planId}/adjust

### Get study summary
# Replace {planId} with the real planId.
GET http://localhost:8081/api/study/plans/e579cbbd-f7e5-4f0a-9432-f49587a3c18f/summary
